tr><tr><td><p>Show in funnel</p></td><td><p>Select the checkbox to enable corresponding stage in the \"Sales Pipeline\" dashboard.</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Show in progress bar</p></td><td><p>Select the checkbox to enable corresponding stage on the workflow bar of the opportunity page. The column is not displayed by default. You can add it manually. Learn more: <a href=\"https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1016#title-756-6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Set up columns</a>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>"
